<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ DJ SERVICE -->
<section class="section dj-service-section" id="dj-service">
  <div class="dj-service-inner">

    <div class="dj-service-text">
      <div class="section-label">DJ Service</div>
      <h2><span class="grad">The Fam Jam Sound</span></h2>
      <p class="dj-big-sub">Not a playlist. An actual DJ set built around your party.</p>

      <p class="dj-body">You tell us what you want to hear — favorite artists, must-plays, genres to avoid — and we build around it. We go through your wishlist before the event, then read the room and adjust on the fly.</p>

      <p class="dj-body">We've pulled off 80s rock, emo, showtunes, and 90s pop in the same night. We've also started a set as a rave and switched to indie rock halfway through because that's where the crowd wanted to go. Whatever you bring us, we'll make it work.</p>

      <ul class="dj-features">
        <li>Three DJs rotating through every event</li>
        <li>Pioneer XDJ-AZ system + table, brought and set up by us</li>
        <li>JBL PartyBox 310 — more than enough for most events (larger PA rental available for bigger venues)</li>
        <li>Fog machine + lasers and lights for night events (full lighting package available if you want to go bigger)</li>
        <li>Microphone on-hand for speeches and toasts</li>
        <li>Day-of announcing and scripting included</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="dj-closer">Tell us the moments that matter. We'll make sure they land.</p>

      <div class="dj-included-box">
        <div class="dj-included-label">✦ Day-of Scripting — Included</div>
        <p>Have moments you don't want to miss? Share your timeline and we'll work them in. We can follow your script or help you build one — either way, we keep things moving so you're not watching the clock.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dj-service-visual">
      <div class="dj-main-image">
        <img src="/images/dj-hero.jpg" alt="Fam Jam DJs at the decks">
      </div>
      <div class="dj-image-pair">
        <div class="dj-thumb">
          <img src="/images/dj-setup.jpg" alt="DJ setup">
        </div>
        <div class="dj-thumb">
          <img src="/images/dj-in-action.jpg" alt="DJ in action">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dj-price-badge">
        <div class="dj-price-amount">$600</div>
        <div class="dj-price-label">3 hours · DJ Service</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
